>>Services

`a`Ffff

Chicago Offline runs several services for the mesh
community. All are open and free to use.

`F0cf
-

>Reticulum Network

`F3f1  >>  `!`FfffTransport Node`!
`Ffff     Routes traffic, relays announces, serves paths.
     TCP entrypoint on port 4242.

`F3f1  >>  `!`FfffLXMF Propagation`!
`Ffff     Stores and forwards encrypted messages for
     offline users. Your messages wait here until
     the recipient comes online.

`F3f1  >>  `!`FfffNomadNet Node`!
`Ffff     You're reading it. Pages served over Reticulum.

`F3f1  >>  `!`FfffRelay Chat (rrcd)`! `Ffb3`!LIVE`!
`Ffff     Real-time IRC-style chat rooms over Reticulum.
     Hub: `Ffb3Chicago Offline`Ffff
     Hash: `Ffb3215f9cc1867ea027cdddfe459bce3033
`Ffff     Join `!chicagooffline`! — clients auto-discover the hub.

