>Observer Firmware

`Ffff
Pre-configured MeshCore MQTT observer firmware for
Chicagoland. Supports Heltec V3/V4, WSL3, Station G2.
Auto-connects to LetsMesh, ChiMesh, and Chicago Offline
broker networks.

     `Ffb3 chicagooffline.com/observers

